\pard\sl240\slmult1\cf1\b\f0\fs24             there is never a complete turnover in the membership of the official board in one year. Also, many churches have adopted a policy that permits a deacon to serve for two consecutive three-year terms, after which he must remain inactive for at\cf0\b0\f1\fs12\par

