\pard\fi254\li1732\ri311\sb1\sl302\slmult0\qj\cf1\b\f0\fs24 The deacon board should meet at least once a month. The pastor is the chairman of the board and may call special meetings when the occasion requires.\cf0\b0\f1\fs22\par

\pard\fi254\li1761\ri301\sb5\sl304\slmult0\qj\cf1\b\f0\fs24 In the annual business meeting of the church, a financial report should be given to the congregation of all the financial activity of the church.  Major decisions such as acquiring church property should have the approval of the entire con-\cf0\b0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\b\f0\fs24 gregation in a business meeting, even though it may be neces-\cf0\b0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\b\f0\fs24 sary to call a special meeting for the purpose.\cf0\b0\f1\fs22\par

\pard\fi263\li1780\ri296\sb1\sl302\slmult0\qj\cf1\b\f0\fs24 In business meetings of the church, and in the monthly board meetings, the general procedures of parliamentary \super\fs36 law \nosupersub\fs24 should be followed.\cf0\b0\f1\fs22\par

