\pard\li10\sb21\sl211\slmult0\cf1\b\f0\fs26 A \i\fs24 Guide to Church Planting\cf0\b0\i0\f1\fs22\par

\pard\sl240\slmult1\fs12\par

\pard\li2635\ri127\sb169\sl275\slmult0\qj\cf1\b\f0\fs26 tion \fs24 of witnessing laymen. The leaders must see to it that the local church program provides opportunities for such involve-\cf0\b0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\b\f0\fs24 ment. A good motto: Every church a growing church with every member a witness.\cf0\b0\f1\fs22\par

\pard\fi263\li2692\ri94\sb74\sl295\slmult0\qj\cf1\b\f0\fs24 Methods and equipment will not take the place of the \cf0\b0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\b\f0\fs24 Holy Spirit. In order for evangelism to be effective it must be \cf0\b0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\b\f0\fs24 carried on with divine enablement. Nevertheless, the church \cf0\b0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\b\f0\fs24 has before it today open doors of which past generations did \cf0\b0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\b\f0\fs24 not even dream. We have modern transportation that enables \cf0\b0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\b\f0\fs24 us to reach the remotest parts of the world. The printing\cf0\b0\f1\fs22\par

\pard\li2745\ri90\sb4\sl294\slmult0\qj\cf1\b\f0\fs24 press, radio, television, and public address systems can all be used to speed the eternal gospel of Jesus Christ. Coupled with this, God has sent His Spirit to give spiritual enablement to His church. The church must take seriously its commission \fs26 to fulfill \fs24 its God-given task in today's world.\cf0\b0\f1\fs22\par

\pard\li12662\sl644\slmult0\fs24\page\par
\par

\pard\li2890\sb362\sl644\slmult0\cf1\f0\fs56 10\cf0\f1\fs22\par

\pard\li1176\sb223\sl414\slmult0\cf1\b\f0\fs36 Self-Continuity Functions\cf0\b0\f1\fs22\par

\pard\li10\ri515\sb287\sl292\slmult0\qj\cf1\b\f0 WE HAVE SEEN \fs24 that the reason-for-being functions of the \cf0\b0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\expndtw-1\b\f0\fs24 church are to worship and glorify God, to buildup the church, \cf0\expndtw0\b0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\b\f0\fs24 and to evangelize the world. These functions must be kept \cf0\b0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\b\dn4\f0\fs24 primary. There are also self-continuity functions in which \cf0\b0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\b\f0\fs24 a church must engage in order to carry out the reason-for-\cf0\b0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\b\f0\fs26 being \fs24 functions. These have to do with the administration of\cf0\b0\f1\fs22\par

