\pard\fi647\li135\ri1998\sb116\sl249\slmult0\qj\cf1\expndtw1\f0\fs18 The Old Testament \super\fs27 presented the church in typological \cf0\expndtw0\nosupersub\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs18 form. Sample types might \super\fs27 include Ruth, the Gentile bride and \cf0\nosupersub\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs18 Israel, God's remnant in the wor\super\fs27 ld.\cf0\nosupersub\f1\fs22\par

