\pard\li10\ri899\sb86\sl255\slmult0\qj\cf1\dn4\f0\fs22 seems inappropriate to move on to matters of team leadership \cf0\f1\line\cf1\f0 before examining that golden deposit of truth, Ephesians \fs20 4:11-\cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs20 16, \fs22 which speaks so clearly regarding the church's educational \cf0\f1\line\cf1\f0 task. Note carefully the \i New International Version \i0 translation of \cf0\f1\line\cf1\expndtw1\f0 the passage:\cf0\expndtw0\f1\par

