\pard\li2241\sl220\slmult0\fs24\par

\pard\li2865\ri1320\sb33\sl220\slmult0\qj\cf1\f0\fs20 nity corporately as a community. Real personal Christian living individually and corporately as a community that rests upon the individual's and the community's personal relationship with a personal God gives us the possibility of Christian community before the eye of an observing worlds\cf0\f1\fs22\par

