\pard\li3912\ri561\sl168\slmult0\qj\cf1\f0\fs14 anything else, he draws a blueprint\f2\emdash\f0 a plan. The prospective home owner thus knows generally what it will look like before he actually builds it. The home owner considers how much room he will \i need. \i0 if he has a \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs14 family of six and will do a lot of entertaining, he will need to build a \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs14 larger house. Thus, the plan must correspond with the purpose. Even if one does not draw a project on paper, he has planned it in his mind. You must think out certain factors before you act. This kind of planning is necessary for all the development and activities of the church.\cf0\f1\fs22\par

