\pard\li3542\sb9\sl138\slmult0\cf1\f0\fs12 Functions of Planning\cf0\f1\fs22\par

\pard\fi182\li3513\ri359\sb93\sl172\slmult0\qj\cf1\f0\fs12 Planning that is done by an individual, a group, or a church should be \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\dn4\f0\fs12 done in answer to two questions: When is it done, and how is it done?\cf0\f1\fs22\par

\pard\fi201\li3480\ri383\sb83\sl171\slmult0\qj\cf1\up0\f0\fs12 The "when" of any plan, of course, depends on "what" needs to be \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 planned. If the subject concerned is the Christian education program, then \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 it will probably follow the school year. If it is the church budget, it may \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 follow the calendar or fiscal year. The primary concern about "when" is \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 for the planning to be done enough in advance to be of value. To start \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 planning two weeks before you want to hold a city-wide evangelistic \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 campaign would certainly be useless. We will discuss this subject more in this lesson when we consider scheduling.\cf0\f1\fs22\par

\pard\fi206\li3441\ri451\sb85\sl169\slmult0\qj\cf1\f0\fs12 If a planning group is responsible for needs that cover the year, the \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 group should meet before the year begins and work out a plan. Some \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 projects or situations may require a five year plan, a yearly plan, or a \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 quarterly plan. If your church is new and your planning committees are \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 new, it is best that their first experience of planning be a small project o\super\fs18 r \cf0\nosupersub\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 for a short time period.\cf0\f1\fs22\par

\pard\fi206\li3403\ri508\sb87\sl168\slmult0\qj\cf1\f0\fs12 Scheduling time is a major consideration for planni\super\fs18 ng, for this you \cf0\nosupersub\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 need a master calendar. This is a calendar \super\fs18 on which every church function \nosupersub\fs12 is scheduled so that any group making plans can co\super\fs18 nsult the calendar and \cf0\nosupersub\f1\fs22\line\cf1\i\f0\fs12 avoid \i0 the problem of time conflicts or duplication of effort.\cf0\f1\fs22\par

\pard\li3571\sb111\sl138\slmult0\cf1\f0\fs12 When we look at how planning is done, we should f\super\fs18 ollow certain steps:\cf0\nosupersub\f1\fs22\par

