\pard\fi206\li10\ri1741\sb104\sl195\slmult0\qj\cf1\f0\fs14 1. \i Job descriptions. \i0 How would you feel if you were told to do \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs14 something and you were not told exactly what was expected of you? That \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs14 would be frustrating. A job description provides the description of duties, \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs14 responsibilities, and lines of authority. The following items are usually\cf0\f1\fs22\par

