\pard\fi182\li3532\ri501\sl183\slmult0\qj\cf1\f0\fs12 Who is responsible to define jobs? Situations vary with each church, so \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 this must be flexible. Sometimes a board or a committee.defines the job. \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 If you arc starting a new church, you may have to do it. If the position \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 already exists, the person who is in \i the \i0 position \i may \i0 be \i the \i0 best one to \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 describe it. Once a job description is made, the supervising person should \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 sit down with the person involved and go through it with them to be sure \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 he understands it clearly.\cf0\f1\fs22\par

\pard\fi187\li3523\ri558\sb97\sl187\slmult0\qj\cf1\expndtw1\f0\fs12 2. \i Coordinate responsibilities. \i0 It is very interesting to note how \cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 coordinated a healthy body is. The relationship of \i the \i0 different parts of \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 the human body shows how each part has a responsibility to some other \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\expndtw1\f0\fs12 part. That is how relationships should be coordinated in the church \cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 body.--for each part is responsible to and dependent on another part.\cf0\f1\fs22\par

\pard\fi196\li3480\ri615\sb177\sl183\slmult0\qj\cf1\f0\fs12 Suppose there is a Sunday School teacher in your church who needs \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 coloring pencils for his class. How does he know whom \fs8 to \fs12 ask for the \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 pencils? If not you, who? If many people in your church have similar \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 types of questions, you will have problems on your hands. By clarifying \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 lines of responsibility, each one understands how he fits in the chain of \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 relationship which is described as either a line of authority or a line of \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\expndtw1\f0\fs12 consultation. We may not be able to describe all the aspects of an \cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 organization fully with a paper chart because of some complexities and \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\expndtw1\f0\fs12 changes that occur from time to time. In fact, the dynamics of an \cf0\expndtw0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 organization requite the chart to be changed and improved as needed. The \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 chart's main purpose is to give a picture of how tasks are allocated and \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 how they relate to each other.\cf0\f1\fs22\par

\pard\li3470\ri717\sb120\sl153\slmult0\qj\cf1\f0\fs12 7 Circle the letter of each CORRECT completion. In relationships each \cf0\f1\fs22\line\cf1\f0\fs12 participant needs to understand\cf0\f1\fs22\par

\pard\li3465\ri1230\sb12\sl163\slmult0\qj\cf1\b\f0\fs12 a \b0   how he fits in the organization and to whom he is responsible. b   the limits of his authority and how to maintain control.\cf0\f1\fs22\par

\pard\li3456\sb16\sl138\slmult0\cf1\f0\fs12 c   what is expected of him.\cf0\f1\fs22\par

